          One verb. <span class="italic text-muted-foreground">Register.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-md font-sans leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          Every product that watches the world rebuilds the same stack: schedulers, LLM tool loops,
