        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <%= link_to "Full docs", marketing_docs_path, class: "rounded-md border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2.5 font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-widest transition hover:border-primary/40" %>
          <%= link_to "OpenAPI spec", cloud_app_url("/api/v1/openapi.yaml"), class: "rounded-md border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2.5 font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-widest transition hover:border-primary/40" %>
          <%= link_to "GitHub repo", github_repo_url, class: "rounded-md border border-border bg-card px-4 py-2.5 font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-widest transition hover:border-primary/40", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-border px-5 py-3">
          <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground"><%= URI(meerkat_cloud_url).host %>/api/v1</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-primary">v1 · stable</span>
        </div>
        <div class="divide-y divide-border">
          <% [
            ["POST", "/api/v1/signup", "Create account + API key"],
            ["POST", "/api/v1/tasks", "Register a task — recurring or one_off"],
            ["POST", "/api/v1/tasks/:id/run", "Trigger an on-demand run"],
            ["GET ", "/api/v1/tasks/:id/runs", "Stream execution history"],
            ["GET ", "/api/v1/tasks/:id/events", "Audit log + webhook deliveries"],
            ["POST", "/api/v1/tasks/:id/pause", "Pause a recurring schedule"]
          ].each do |method, path, desc| %>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-[70px_minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(0,1.4fr)] items-center gap-4 px-5 py-4 transition hover:bg-background/40">
              <span class="font-mono text-[11px] font-bold <%= method.strip == "POST" ? "text-primary" : "text-accent" %>"><%= method %></span>
              <code class="font-mono text-[13px] text-foreground"><%= path %></code>
              <span class="text-[13px] text-muted-foreground"><%= desc %></span>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-border py-32">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid opacity-40"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: var(--gradient-glow)"></div>
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
    <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary">$ meerkat init</p>
    <h2 class="mt-6 font-serif text-[clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4.5rem)] leading-[1] tracking-tight">
      Stop building the same async stack.<br>
      <span class="italic text-gradient-amber" data-typewriter="register a task →"></span><span class="cursor-blink"></span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-xl leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
      Sign up free, connect your LLM key, and ship your first webhook in under five minutes.
      Or deploy the open source version yourself — same API, your infrastructure.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
      <%= link_to marketing_signup_label, marketing_signup_path, marketing_signup_link_options(class: "rounded-md bg-primary px-6 py-3.5 font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-primary-foreground transition hover:brightness-110 glow-amber") %>
      <%= link_to "Read the docs", marketing_docs_path, class: "rounded-md border border-border bg-card px-6 py-3.5 font-mono text-sm font-semibold transition hover:border-primary/40" %>
      <%= link_to "★ Star on GitHub", github_repo_url, class: "rounded-md border border-border bg-card px-6 py-3.5 font-mono text-sm font-semibold transition hover:border-primary/40", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%= render "marketing/footer" %>
